nodes.text: The house of Parnelli was an ancient noble house. It funded the construction of the Parnelli Museum of Art, which was named for the house, in the capital city of Theed on the planet Naboo. The museum was completed by 32 BBY.
The house of Parnelli was first mentioned in Nexus of Power, a 2016 supplement to Fantasy Flight Games' Star Wars: Force and Destiny.
